    <title>创建属于自己的BLOG</title>
    <link href="/csblog/2020/04/23/%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2blog/"/>
    <url>/csblog/2020/04/23/%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2blog/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>1.安装Node.js(过程省略)</p><p>2.查看Node.js的版本</p><pre><code class="hljs shell">node -v</code></pre><p>3.查看npm的版本</p><pre><code class="hljs shell">npm -v</code></pre><p>4.切换成国内的打包工具(淘宝源)</p><pre><code class="hljs shell"><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash">获取原本镜像地址</span>npm get registry <span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash">设为淘宝镜像</span>npm config set registry http://registry.npm.taobao.org/</code></pre><p>5.安装博客的框架(hexo)</p><pre><code class="hljs shell">npm install hexo-cli -ghexo init blogcd blognpm installhexo server</code></pre><p>6.发布博客的内容会出现错误没设置gitee的账号密码</p><pre><code class="hljs shell">hexo ggit config --global user.name "cui"git config --global user.email "1729917782@qq.com"</code></pre><p>7.</p>]]></content>
    
    
    
